  "text": "Nowadays we interpret this quite literally as the perturbative expansion of an open string theory, either because the full open string theory is just equal to the gauge theory (as e.g. for Chern-Simons theory [CITATION_1] ), or because we take an appropriate low-energy limit (as e.g. for N = 4 SYM [CITATION_2] ).",
